1. *Očiju* mi je zaslepio sjaj sunca. (My eyes were blinded by the sun's shine.)
2. U *očijima* joj se ogledala tuga. (Sadness was reflected in her eyes.)
3. *Očima* je pratio let ptica. (He followed the birds' flight with his eyes.)
4. *Očima* sam pregledao ceo prostor. (I looked over the whole space with my eyes.)
5. Pravio je krugove *očima*. (He was making circles with his eyes.)